questions.text:
What is the output of this code?
```dart
int x = 10;
if (x > 5) {
  print('A');
} else if (x > 8) {
  print('B');
} else {
  print('C');
}
```

How many times will this loop execute?
```dart
int i = 0;
while (i < 5) {
  print(i);
  i++;
}
```

What will be the output?
```dart
for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  if (i == 1) continue;
  print(i);
}
```

How many times will this do-while loop execute?
```dart
int i = 10;
do {
  print(i);
  i++;
} while (i < 5);
```

What is the output of this nested loop?
```dart
for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
  for (int j = 0; j < 2; j++) {
    print('$i$j');
  }
}
```

What is the output?
```dart
int x = 5;
switch (x) {
  case 1:
  case 2:
  case 3:
    print('Small');
    break;
  case 4:
  case 5:
    print('Medium');
    break;
  default:
    print('Large');
}
```
